rwchcd: a central heating controller daemon for rWCHC

Dependencies: libglib2.0-dev wiringpi pkg-config
Documentation deps: doxygen graphviz

To build, run 'make'
To install, as root run 'make install'
To uninstall, as root run 'make uninstall'
To generate documentation, run 'make doc'

A systemd service file is provided that will be installed when running
'make install'. The daemon will be started at next reboot unless manually
started with systemctl start rwchcd.service

The D-Bus interface exposed by the daemon are presented in the
rwchcd_introspection.xml file.

Examples:
dbus-send --print-reply --system --dest=org.slashdirt.rwchcd \
        --type=method_call /org/slashdirt/rwchcd \
        org.slashdirt.rwchcd.Control.SysmodeSet byte:2

dbus-send --print-reply --system --dest=org.slashdirt.rwchcd \
        --type=method_call /org/slashdirt/rwchcd \
        org.slashdirt.rwchcd.Control.ToutdoorGet
